            <run fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontsize='12'>, highlighting </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontsize='12'>customer segments, purchasing frequency, spending patterns, and high-value customers</run>
            <run fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontsize='12'>. It enables identification of </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontsize='12'>loyal, at-risk, and high-value customers</run>
            <run fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontsize='12'> to support targeted marketing strategies and improve customer retention.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
